c: 16
v: 125
t: "Ŵilanjilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) kwitala lya Ambuje ŵenu mwa lunda lwakusokoka ni kaŵilanjile kambone, soni ponyanganani nao maloŵe kaponyangane kambone, chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵaakwamanya chenene ŵaasokonecheele kuleka litala Lyakwe, soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakwamanya chenene ŵali ŵakongoka"